<title>DWELLING IN BEULAH LAND</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gam lataka pata kidona thawmgi chuh ka zai,
 Lei gitloh na'n muntin a zel suok hi tih ka hei;
 Ginlahna, lauhna, lei thil hawn ei subuoi thei puon au,
 Ei sulawk pha puon au, Beulah Gamah.

[V2]
 Van mei kaih lohna munah, tang chung a chun ka cheng hi,
 Tuikhuk a tui chuh ka dawn, kan tikni neilo ding;
 Aw ahi, Manna'n ka kivak hi, kiem leh tawmtik nei ngeilo,
 Beulah gama cheng ka hih ziekin.

[V3]
 2. Nuoilam gamla tak khawvel ah ginlahna huihpi nung,
 Mihiem chate chun a galteu chuh a do zing ui;
 Pathien thu kulhpi sung achun bittak in ka um hi,
 Bangmah sukbuoi phakloh, Beulah Gam ah.

[V4]
 3. Huihpi chuh nung mahleh agi chun ei sulau puona,
 Pathien khuta chuh venin bittak in ka um hi;
 Nisa a vak zing hi, bangman ei suna thei puona,
 Kumkhuon ka bit zing hi, Beulah Gam ah.

[V5]
 4. Pathien nasep haw ka etin tupna dettak ka nei,
 A aw nem chuh ka zai, A lampi siem chuh ka mui;
 Thagau a umin hukdamna umchan bukim ka sin,
 Kipak takin chawl ka, Beulah Gam ah.</lyrics>
</song>